stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Unprovisioned: DCU Boot

    Unprovisioned --> Provisioned: FC-1 sends 0xF0A1<br/>(HMAC + bastion + client key)

    state Provisioned {
        [*] --> Idle
        Idle --> TunnelActive: Phone-home trigger<br/>0xF0A0 accepted
        TunnelActive --> Idle: Tunnel closes<br/>(timeout/disconnect)
    }

    Provisioned --> Degraded: Health check 0xF0A2<br/>status != 0x00

    state Degraded {
        [*] --> MissingHMAC: status 0x01
        [*] --> MissingKey: status 0x02
        [*] --> MissingSSH: status 0x03
    }

    Degraded --> Provisioned: FC-1 re-provisions<br/>0xF0A1

    Provisioned --> Unprovisioned: DCU restart<br/>(if HMAC not on disk)

    note right of Unprovisioned
        FC-1 health check runs
        every 5 minutes.
        Detects DCU restart via
        uptime field in 0xF0A2
        response.
    end note
